Exact Simulation of Noncircular or Improper Complex-Valued Stationary Gaussian Processes using Circulant Embedding

by Adam M. Sykulski and Donald B. Percival (2016)

email: a.sykulski@lancaster.ac.uk with queries

Here we provide a MATLAB .m file named improper.m for simulating series from a complex-valued stationary Gaussian process with specified autocovariance and complementary covariance
